dct_title_s: New York and New Jersey Boundary 1887
dct_description_sm: Map of the boundary line between the states of New York and New Jersey in lands under water in Raritan Bay. Includes list of commissioners for each state involved in the final approval of this map. Scales in both land and nautical miles.
